  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they had me-- so we had-- they picked from a few thousand people this amount.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we went to Italy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "American trucks.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] American trucks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we-- they dropped us off in Santa Maria.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was the town, a small town on the ocean.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Beautiful.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And they put us in in a house, alone, a private house.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think if it's right that I remember right that this was a German, a big, rich millionaire.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was living on this mountain.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the water's down there, beautiful all the way around with the grapefruit-- not grapefruit--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- I'm a [? little out. ?]",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not little ones.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not grapefruit.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, grapefruit.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's what it is.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Grapefruit, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So around there in a big lake [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] and the ocean on this side.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And what they did is I think they said, you're gonna get food.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You have to cook for yourself, and we're gonna talk to you later.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Don't worry, everything is OK.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You're going to get everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Cook and eat and that's it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And some other people are gonna see you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the other people were two people that the-- from the Haganah or whatever.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they said, you people have a mission.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You have a mission.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So now, this house was not far that you can go into the water.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So you needed a--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--a boat or something.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this house was good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The boat could go underneath the house, you know, it had the bridge over it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this owner, the guy who had, was placed space for three cars-- for three boats.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had amazing just a few people, not the-- not the whole group.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
